# Theme
- Smoothie is our custom wrapper around MUI components. We have renamed MUI components like `Dialog` to `Modal`.
- **Use Smoothie over MUI:** we no longer use MUI. Only old code can use MUI. All MUI components should be imported from Smoothie.

**REMEMBER: Always use Smoothie for new code.**
